  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Working with and training new parents in Nepal</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project has two parts: firstly a campaign to raise awareness and understanding of Down syndrome for new parents of babies with Down syndrome; and secondly intensive training workshops with parents of young children with Down syndrome to provide them with key skills to support their children in their early development. The project will be targeted at parents living in remote areas of Nepal, where information, support and expertise are not available.</narrative>
  </description>
